perminantly change to another namespace:
kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=ingress-ckad

ls /ckad/CKAD202206
vi /ckad/CKAD202206/service.yaml
deployment.spec.template.metadata.labels = service.spec.selector

deployment.spec.template.spec.containers.ports.containerPort = service.spec.ports.targetPort


vi /ckad/CKAD202206/ingress.yaml
spec:
 ingressClassName: traefik
 rules:
 - http:
   paths:
   - path: / 

under service:
name: nginx-ing-svc     //service name


k apply -f /ckad/CKAD202206/service.yaml 
k apply -f /ckad/CKAD202206/ingress.yaml 

//verify
curl -L http://ckad-ingress-test.local


这里deployment正确 所以service file里的selector.app和targetPort要从deployment file读取，ingress file里的path要从deployment中读，service name从service file取
Service 是通过 selector 找 Pod，Pod 的 labels 来自：Deployment → template → metadata → labels
